Package: digiRhythm
Type: Package
Title: Analyzing Animal's Rhythmicity
Version: 1.0
Authors@R: person(given = "Hassan (Roland)",
           family = "Nasser",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "hassan.nasser@me.com",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-1821-3234"))
Author: Hassan (Roland) Nasser <hassan.nasser@me.com>
Maintainer: Hassan (Roland) Nasser <hassan.nasser@me.com>
Description: This package provides a set of tools to analyze and visualize the 
    rhythmic behavior of animals. The main functionalities of this library are: 
    computing the degree of functional coupling and harmonic power, visualizing
    actograms, computing average activity and diurnality index.
